ğŸ’¬ ChatHub â€“ Real-Time MERN Chat Application

ChatHub is a full-stack real-time chat application built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) with Socket.io for instant, bi-directional communication. It allows users to securely register, log in, and chat with others in real time through a modern and responsive interface.

